  "instructions": [
    "In a Talavera plate, heat sesame oil over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add minced garlic and garlic-infused oil, sauté for 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Stir in sliced shiitake mushrooms and diced zucchini, cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and gluten-free soy sauce, bring to a gentle boil then reduce to a simmer.",
    "Add cubed tofu and simmer for 3 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Reduce heat to low and stir in heavy cream and coconut cream until the stew becomes silky and thick.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste, then simmer for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Garnish with sliced scallions and serve hot straight from the Talavera plate."
  ],
